      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Older used car in poor overall condition and priced accordingly. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear, a tired interior, and clear signs of age and use throughout. This is not a clean daily-driver example; it is better suited for someone looking for a budget project, parts car, or inexpensive vehicle who understands it will need attention and repairs. Please come with realistic expectations and inspect it carefully.",
