      "description": "This is an honest project car that is clearly in poor condition and will need significant cosmetic and mechanical attention. It shows substantial wear, age, and deterioration, and it should be approached as a restoration candidate, weekend project, or possible parts car rather than a ready-to-enjoy driver. Expect visible flaws throughout, deferred maintenance, and the likelihood that major systems will need repair, sorting, or full recommissioning. Best suited for a buyer who knows what they\u2019re looking at and wants a car to rebuild to their own standards.",
