    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "A clean, well-kept classic that shows nicely and has the kind of honest appeal that makes it easy to enjoy. This is a solid driver-quality car with good overall presentation, clear signs of care, and plenty of charm without pretending to be a showpiece. It\u2019s the sort of classic you can feel good about driving, enjoying, and improving over time if you choose.",
