    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an approachable price. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability, practicality, and an honest used-car opportunity. A sensible choice for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone seeking inexpensive transportation.",
