    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and could make a great budget commuter, learner car, or weekend project. A straightforward, honest little vehicle for someone who values practicality over polish. If you want inexpensive wheels without spending a fortune, this is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
