      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward driver with strong project potential and solid mechanical character. The powertrain pulls well, the automatic shifts through the range as it should, and the chassis feels composed enough to enjoy as-is while sorting cosmetic and age-related needs over time. A good fit for someone who wants an affordable, usable car with decent bones, simple serviceability, and room to make it their own. Not perfect, but a respectable budget buy with real value for a hands-on owner.",
      "price": 5950.0,
